OL,3,CMPs recommend funding boost to tackle
OL,4,Cparamilitary threat
OL,6,FThe Northern Ireland Affairs Committee
OL,7,Fcommittee has recommended that the
OL,8,FGovernment provide funding to address
OL,9,Ffalling PSNI officer levels.
OL,11,FA boost in funding would help to bring
OL,12,Fofficer levels up to 7,500 as part of
OL,13,Fa strategy to tackle paramilitary
OL,14,Factivity and organised crime, MPs have
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,FThe Westminster committee has
OL,18,Fcautioned that cuts and the lasting
OL,19,Ffinancial ramifications of data leaks
OL,20,Fwill likely see the force shrink to
OL,21,F6,193 officers by April 2025.
