OL,6,FThe New Decade, New Approach deal
OL,7,Fwhich restored the Stormont
OL,8,Fpowersharing institutions in 2020 made
OL,9,Fa commitment that the PSNI should have
OL,10,F7,500 officers.
OL,12,FThe committee's report follows an
OL,13,Finquiry into the effect of
OL,14,Fparamilitary activity and organised
OL,15,Fcrime.
OL,17,FThe report said that the continued
OL,18,Fpresence of paramilitary groups, 25
OL,19,Fyears on from the Good Friday
OL,20,FAgreement, represents a "festering
OL,21,Fwound on society in Northern Ireland".
