OL,6,FDuring its evidence sessions, the PSNI
OL,7,Ftold the committee that planned cuts
OL,8,Fare expected to lead to 75 fewer
OL,9,Fneighbourhood officers and 96 fewer
OL,10,Fserious crimes detectives, conceding
OL,11,Fthat their responsiveness would be
OL,12,Fimpacted.
OL,14,FThe report said low prosecution rates
OL,15,Fof violent crime discourages people
OL,16,Ffrom reporting crimes and allows
OL,17,Fparamilitary groups to "act with
OL,18,Fimpunity".
