OL,3,CMPs recommend funding boost to tackle
OL,4,Cparamilitary threat
OL,6,FIt has called on the UK Government to
OL,7,Fwork with Stormont to help improve
OL,8,Fclearance rates for paramilitary-style
OL,9,Fattacks.
OL,11,FIt has also advocated Westminster
OL,12,Fsupporting Stormont's Department of
OL,13,FJustice to take a "safeguarding
OL,14,Fapproach" to the issue, opening the
OL,15,Fway to more convictions of those
OL,16,Finvolved in paramilitary activity on
OL,17,Fthe grounds of coercion, modern
OL,18,Fslavery and child criminal
OL,19,Fexploitation.
