OL,4,Cparamilitary threat
OL,6,FMPs heard that among the motivations
OL,7,Ffor the continued existence of armed
OL,8,Fgroups are deprivation, mental health
OL,9,Fissues and psychological trauma, while
OL,10,Fmurals glorifying violence can
OL,11,Fretraumatise communities.
OL,13,FIt has called on the UK Government and
OL,14,Fthe executive to commit to a new
OL,15,Fsystem of "trauma-informed practice",
OL,16,Fand to address the socio-economic
OL,17,Fdrivers of paramilitarism.
