OL,6,F"With that in mind, it's concerning
OL,7,Fthat while police numbers in England
OL,8,Fand Wales are set to rise by 20,000,
OL,9,Fthe PSNI's workforce is in decline.
OL,11,F"This is a service depended upon for
OL,12,Fsafety by communities still dealing
OL,13,Fwith persistent paramilitarism."It
OL,14,Ffaces a budgetary black hole, but it
OL,15,Fis one we can ill afford not to fill."
