OL,6,FSir Robert added: "A fully staffed
OL,7,FPSNI would help investigations, but
OL,8,Fprosecution rates for violent crimes
OL,9,Fmust also climb if we're to weaken the
OL,10,Fcoercive power paramilitary groups
OL,11,Fhave over the communities they operate
OL,12,Fin and encourage people to report
OL,13,Fcrimes.
OL,15,F"We need to change the criminal
OL,16,Fjustice mindset and prosecute
OL,17,Fparamilitary groups for coercion,
OL,18,Fmodern slavery and child criminal
OL,19,Fexploitation.
