OL,6,F"However, without addressing the
OL,7,Flonger-term draws to such groups'
OL,8,Fcontinued activity, we will not
OL,9,Feradicate the scourge of
OL,10,Fparamilitarism.
OL,12,F"Deprivation needs to be tackled, with
OL,13,Fbetter access to universal credit, and
OL,14,Fwe need a consistent approach to
OL,15,Fvetting the recipients of public
OL,16,Ffunding, to ensure that taxpayers'
OL,17,Fmoney goes to people who are genuinely
OL,18,Fcommitted to eradicating
OL,19,Fparamilitarism from Northern Ireland.
